#                                QUIC-based active/passive failover daemon
#                                for Solana validators (Go=141 leader bump
#                                continuing Axis 86 Solana SDK Library)
# ============================================================================
#
# UPSTREAM
#   Repository : https://github.com/SOL-Strategies/solana-validator-failover
#   Maintainer : SOL-Strategies
#   License    : MIT
#   Stars      : 22
#   Language   : Go
#   Module     : github.com/sol-strategies/solana-validator-failover
